title: 1.26 Judges I: The Book of Rescuers
itunes:title: Judges I: The Book of Rescuers
description: I wrap-up the Book of Joshua, and rush right into the dark times of the Book of Judges. I start with the central and oldest chapters, called the Book of the Rescuers, the heroic epic of the northern kingdom of Israel.
content:encoded: I wrap-up the Book of Joshua, and rush right into the dark times of the Book of Judges. I start with the central and oldest chapters, called the Book of the Rescuers, the heroic epic of the northern kingdom of Israel.
itunes:subtitle: I finish the real-estate deals in Joshua, and plunge into the excitement of the Book of Judges.
itunes:author: Garry Stevens
